  "description": {
   "en": "(from cdjapan):\nTo what extent can human beings be cruel? Horrific rape and murder and the discrimination against women that underlies it, cult mind control, domestic violence and the murder of a son.... This is a collection of masterful short manga that depicts the abyss of human beings and society as seen through the coverage of real-life incidents. Includes new short stories depicting the post-Fukushima and post-Corona near future.\n\nThe original 2009 release includes:\n- **Their Sins** (彼らの犯罪, Karera no Hanzai) - *Rosa*, December 1992\n- **The Parents . Kill** (親が・殺す, Oya ga . Korosu) - *Rosa*, March 1993\n- **Entrance to Dreams** (夢の入り口, Yume no Iriguchi) - *Belle ROSE*, September 1993\n- **Series . Composition from the Side** (シリーズ・横からの構図, Series. Yoko Kara no Kouzu) - *Human Sexuality*, October 1990, February, May, August 1991, February, May, August 1992"
